  stickyNoteInfos:
  - title: Events + Setters
    position:
      serializedVersion: 2
      x: 1600
      y: -1716
      width: 406
      height: 190
    contents: 'call event from C# like effect.SendEvent("EventName");


      OnJump/OnDash
      will start the system


      if you want to stop them early send the OnStopJump/OnStopDash
      event


      When setting the emission vector, axes shouldnt matter as long
      as the passed vector isn''t emitting into any objects and is normalised'
    theme: Classic
    textSize: Small
    colorTheme: 3
